title: Another champ teaser? More strange symbols on Summoners Rift
body:
I've seen these floating around the map for the past few patches so I tried looking for some info on what it means, but I'm only getting stuff on the bard symbols a few months back. Has anyone seen these or have some extra info for me?

EDIT: It's a conspiracy because the site won't let me post the picture!!
EDIT: Changed it to JPEG and it worked, whoops.
